{"tid":2080321,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：肥佬黎被誣衊坐船「着草」 擬告《大公》《文匯》誹謗 - 李八方","createTime":"2020-06-26T10:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T10:36:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d021e6e2263e9be7ff6d0d26c61fa7966a5b1109","tid":2080321,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T10:36:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200626/756OJXB3TUUTVW4NW2SLODGFUU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200626%2F756OJXB3TUUTVW4NW2SLODGFUU%2F&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2hwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=25671399\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200626%2F756OJXB3TUUTVW4NW2SLODGFUU%2F&h=cb6f03a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200626/756OJXB3TUUTVW4NW2SLODGFUU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：肥佬黎被誣衊坐船「着草」<br />\n擬告《大公》《文匯》誹謗 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/55-7GKwMbM4Soz0Gmkt8I6zfVmY=/955x932/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3RFPCZ4T3VIMHXIXKQTVG43VXQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F55-7GKwMbM4Soz0Gmkt8I6zfVmY%3D%2F955x932%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3RFPCZ4T3VIMHXIXKQTVG43VXQ.gif&h=d47e82ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《大公報》昨日頭版詳細報道「着草」台灣路線，更將矛頭指向黎智英等人。&lt;br /&gt;<br />\n<br />\n左報《大公》同《文匯》噚日自爆「大發現」，話揭發有所謂亂港分子紛紛四出打探逃走門路，仲爆埋幾個偷渡上船熱點，原來所謂嘅逃走「路線」，係偷渡去公海再用駁艇去台灣，雖然左報開頭冇點名係邊個，但就有幅配圖，寫住「嫌疑人遂個捉」，其中之一係壹傳媒創辦人黎智英，另外仲有黃之鋒、陳浩天同李卓人，同時內文特意再加插一段「漢奸黎多次申准離港」。不過黎智英講明一定唔會走，仲話「想創佢個心」！<br />\n<br />\n八方就呢單野問肥佬黎有乜回應，點知佢就劈頭一句鬧返轉頭話對家「想創佢個心」，仲豪氣講「我走咗以後仲使做人？佢都黐嘅」，然後先理性咁分析，自己如果咁一走了次，唔只名譽冇晒，連《蘋果日報》嘅誠信同信譽都冇埋，甚至會拖累埋泛民主派，「佢（中共）就當然想我走啦，作得過就作！」最後仲好認真咁警告，話已經問過法律意見，「可以告佢，我會告佢。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hlyvjIx5GtFJ2gU05AZcOBhFgJU=/869x711/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TQUJ7QNZDOZ6DQ2YJO5Q4EF2YE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhlyvjIx5GtFJ2gU05AZcOBhFgJU%3D%2F869x711%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTQUJ7QNZDOZ6DQ2YJO5Q4EF2YE.gif&h=8030e52c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《文匯》快訊亦登出相同報道。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒拒未戰先降<br />\n<br />\n其實唔止肥佬黎唔會走，黃之鋒<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n冇退縮嘅理由。<br />\n<br />\n八方睇返篇個報道，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n，係咪要快啲邀請有關記者協助調查呢？<br />\n<br />\n李八方"}]}